
Auth	

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

POST	/api/auth/register/user	Register a new user	registerValidation, validateRequest
POST	/api/auth/register/vendor	Register a new vendor	registerValidation, validateRequest
POST	/api/auth/register/admin	Register a new admin	registerValidation, validateRequest
POST	/api/auth/verify-otp	Verify OTP for registration	None
POST	/api/auth/login/user	User login	loginValidation, validateRequest
POST	/api/auth/login/vendor	Vendor login	loginValidation, validateRequest
POST	/api/auth/login/admin	Admin login	loginValidation, validateRequest

Product	

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

POST /api/product/	


Create a new product (with multiple images)	verifyToken, authMiddleware, roleMiddleware

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

GET	/api/product/	Get all products	None
GET	/api/product/:id	Get a product by ID	None
PUT	/api/product/:id	Update a product by ID (with image uploads)	verifyToken, authMiddleware, roleMiddleware
DELETE	/api/product/:id	Delete a product by ID	verifyToken, authMiddleware, roleMiddleware
POST	/api/product/:id/rate	Add a rating to a product	verifyToken, authMiddleware, roleMiddleware


Seller	

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

POST	/api/seller/register	Register a user as a seller	verifyToken, authMiddleware, roleMiddleware
GET	/api/seller/:sellerId	Get seller details by ID	verifyToken, authMiddleware, roleMiddleware
PUT	/api/seller/:sellerId	Update seller profile	verifyToken, authMiddleware, roleMiddleware
POST	/api/seller/add-product	  Add a product to sellers store	verifyToken, authMiddleware, roleMiddleware
POST	/api/seller/transaction	Handle wallet transactions for seller	verifyToken, authMiddleware, roleMiddleware


Category

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

POST	/api/category/	Create a new category	verifyToken, authMiddleware, roleMiddleware
GET	/api/category/	Get all categories	None
GET	/api/category/:id	Get a category by ID	None
PUT	/api/category/:id	Update a category by ID	verifyToken, authMiddleware, roleMiddleware
DELETE	/api/category/:id	Delete a category by ID	verifyToken, authMiddleware, roleMiddleware



